'''飓风伊莎贝尔对纽约州和新英格兰的影响'''相对较小，并且主要局限于风害。[[飓风伊莎贝尔|飓风伊莎贝尔]]于2003年9月6日在[[大西洋|大西洋]]热带海域的[[佛得角|佛得角]]附近由一股[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成。系统朝西北方向前进，进入一片水温较高且[[风切变|风切变]]很弱的环境后稳步加强，于9月11日达到风速每小时270[[公里|公里]]的最高强度。经过四天的强度波动后，飓风逐渐减弱，于9月18日在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]以风速每小时165公里的强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。风暴登陆后迅速减弱，于次日在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]西部转变为[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

[[纽约州|纽约州]]受到的损失共计达到9000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|90000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="tcr">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven & Hugh Cobb |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Tropical Cyclone Report |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131114014935/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003isabel.shtml |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-11-14 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003isabel.shtml?}}</ref>，[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]也报告了约10万美元损失（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|100000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）。中等强度的大风刮断了该地区的许多供电线路，导致局部地区停电，还有两人因[[风暴|风暴]]产生的大浪而遇难。

== 防灾措施 ==
飓风伊莎贝尔在北卡罗莱纳州登陆前数小时，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]向[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]和纽约州边界到[[苏福克县_(纽约州)|苏福克县]][[莫里切斯_(纽约州)|莫里切斯]]（{{lang|en|Moriches}}）之间的[[长岛_(纽约)|长岛]]南部海岸发布了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="tcr" />。飓风登岸约一天前，气象预测部门估计风暴有10%的可能性会在距[[纽约市|纽约市]]不到120公里处经过。估计[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]南部其他地区也有类似的概率，伊莎贝尔还有3%的可能性会在距[[缅因州|缅因州]]的[[东港_(缅因州)|东港]]不到120公里处经过<ref name="prob45">{{cite web|author=Beven |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Probabilities 45 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-15 |archivedate=2013-06-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617202131/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/prb/al132003.prblty.045.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/prb/al132003.prblty.045.shtml? }}</ref>。从飓风吹袭陆地约两天前开始直到其登岸数小时后，气象预测部门都估计风暴将在穿越纽约州西部上空的过程中逐渐转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，然后以温带系统形式进入[[加拿大|加拿大]]<ref name="archive">{{cite web |author=National Hurricane Center |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Advisory Archive |accessdate=2014-02-15 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/ISABEL.shtml |archivedate=2013-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001132223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/ISABEL.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

[[纽约州州长|纽约州州长]][[乔治·保陶基|乔治·保陶基]]敦促居民购买紧急救援物资，并给汽车加满[[汽油|汽油]]。纽约州应急管理办公室从风暴登岸前一星期就开始着手准备应对这场飓风。该办公室还发布了第一级应急启动，由策划小组准备好应急预案，并努力协调州内其他部门。纽约州[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]开始进行前期准备工作，检查能够在紧急情况下动员的人员名单。陆地和空中国民警卫队官员确定紧急情况下需要动用的设备，如[[直升机|直升机]]、[[发电机|发电机]]、高车轴车辆和通讯器材等。州警务人员根据需要制订了人员和设备的应急计划。纽约州公园、休闲和历史保护办事处确保需要的设备都能正常使用，还用沙袋对建筑物进行固定来应对可能出现的洪灾。<ref name="nysdot">{{cite web |author=Office of Media Relations |date=2003-09-16 |title=Governor Pataki Announces State Gearing Up for Isabel |publisher=New York State Department of Transportation |accessdate=2014-02-15 |url=https://www.dot.ny.gov/news/press-releases/2003/2003209 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517140730/https://www.dot.ny.gov/news/press-releases/2003/2003209 |dead-url=no }}</ref>七家航空公司允许可能会受到飓风影响的旅客推迟登机日期<ref name="airtravel">{{cite web |author=Air Travel.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515054337/http://airtravel.about.com/cs/airtravellinks/a/hurricane.htm |year=2003 |title=Changing Tickets in the Path of a Hurricane |accessdate=2014-02-15 |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no |url=http://airtravel.about.com/cs/airtravellinks/a/hurricane.htm}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Isabel_2003_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
伊莎贝尔和一个[[高压脊|高压脊]]之间的[[压力梯度|压力梯度]]给纽约州东南部大部分地区带去了至少有热带风暴强度的东北风<ref name="nycncdc">{{cite web |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Southeast New York |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]]}}</ref>。辛纳科克水湾记录到的阵风时速为84[[公里|公里]]<ref name="tcr" />，另一个位于[[拉瓜地亚机场|拉瓜地亚机场]]的监测站记录到的阵风时速则为82公里<ref name="nycncdc" />，该机场的航班也出现了平均达到90[[分钟|分钟]]的诞误<ref name="cnn918">{{cite web |author=CNN.com |date=2003-09-19 |title=Isabel snarls air traffic in the East |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030920190345/http://edition.cnn.com/2003/TRAVEL/09/18/isabel.travel/ |accessdate=2014-02-15 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2003/TRAVEL/09/18/isabel.travel/ |archivedate=2003-09-20}}</ref>。最强的风力由飓风的外围[[雨带|雨带]]产生，刮倒了许多树木，还刮断了许多树枝和电线。中等强度的大风在[[纽约都会区|纽约都会区]]刮倒了640棵树和801截树枝。一位开车途经[[纳苏县_(纽约州)|纳苏县]][[大颈庄园|大颈庄园]]（{{lang|en|Great Neck Estates}}）的男子因树枝砸在车上而身受重伤。此外还有一截掉落的树枝砸在一位男子头部，导致了严重的头部损伤<ref name="nycncdc" />。纽约市及其周边有约110万用户失去电力供应，不过大部分都在飓风过境次日恢复<ref name="market">{{cite web |author=CNN News |year=2003 |title=State-by-state assessment of damage from Isabel |accessdate=2008-02-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080227005827/http://www.sunbeltrentals.com/news/HurricaneIsabelAftermath.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.sunbeltrentals.com/news/HurricaneIsabelAftermath.pdf |archivedate=2008-02-27}}</ref>。

[[长滩_(纽约州)|长滩]]（{{lang|en|Long Beach}}）近海有一位男子在徒手[[冲浪|冲浪]]时因遇上大浪而丧生<ref name="nycncdc" />。更加西北方向的内陆风力较弱，不过该州中南部部分地点还是有树木被风刮倒。[[斯科哈里县_(纽约州)|斯科哈里县]][[科布尔斯基尔|科布尔斯基尔]]（{{lang|en|Cobleskill}}）有一辆汽车被倒下的树砸中而受损。强风还导致什科哈里（{{lang|en|Schoharie}}）和莫霍克瓦利（{{lang|en|Mohawk Valleys}}）东部有约3000户居民家中停电<ref name="snyncdc">{{cite web |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for South-Central New York |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。纽约州东北部[[艾塞克斯县_(纽约州)|艾塞克斯县]]的[[莫里亚_(纽约州)|莫里亚]]（{{lang|en|Moriah}}）、[[韦斯特波特_(纽约州)|韦斯特波特]]（{{lang|en|Westport}}）和[[刘易斯_(纽约州)|刘易斯]]（{{lang|en|Lewis}}）三个[[新英格兰镇|小镇]]上都出现了少量树木被吹倒，供电线路被刮断的情况<ref name="nenyncdc">{{cite web |author=NCDC |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Northeast New York |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。全州降雨量普遍较少，只有局部地区报告超过了25毫米<ref name="rain">{{cite web |author=David Roth |year=2005 |title=Rainfall Summary for Hurricane Isabel |publisher=Hydrometeorological Prediction Center |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2013-12-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206140210/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/isabel2003.html |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/isabel2003.html}}</ref>。[[利文斯顿县_(纽约州)|利文斯顿县]]的降雨致使水库溢出，导致了中等程度的洪灾<ref name="ap919">{{cite news |author=Carolyn Thompson |date=2003-09-19 |title=Isabel windy but not as wet in New York |publisher=Associated Press}}</ref>。起初[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]的汽油期货价格因对飓风威胁的预计而上涨，但风暴并没有对炼油设施造成破坏，因此期货价格也相应回落<ref name="nyt">{{cite news |deadurl=no |author=New York Times |title=The Markets: Commodities |accessdate=2014-02-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022111329/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/20/business/the-markets-commodities.html |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/20/business/the-markets-commodities.html | work=The New York Times |archivedate=2012-10-22 |date=2003-09-20}}</ref>。飓风将一些陆地上很少见到的[[鸟类|鸟类]]带到了纽约州西部，其中包括像[[海燕|海燕]]和[[剪嘴鸥|剪嘴鸥]]这样通常只会在咸水区域或开放海域上空发现的鸟，但这些鸟大部分都因栖息地的突然变化而在数天内死去<ref name="bird">{{cite news |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-22590483.html |accessdate=2014-02-15 |author=Buffalo News |date=2003-10-03 |title=Isabel was kind to our region in more ways than one |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611063544/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-22590483.html |archive-date=2014-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。[[卡尤加县_(纽约州)|卡尤加县]]因供电线路被刮倒而引燃了一幢建筑物，造成了轻度烟雾和水害，但幸运的是没有人员因此受伤<ref name="ps920">{{cite news |author=John Stith |date=2003-09-20 |title=Storm Severs Power to Thousands; Firefighters Battle Auburn Apartment Fire Caused By Electrical Problems |publisher=Syracuse Post-Standard}}</ref>。整个纽约州一共遭受了9000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|90000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的经济损失<ref name="tcr" />。

[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]和[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]西部的降雨量达到25毫米<ref name="rain" />。[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[华盛顿县_(罗德岛州)|华盛顿县]]的[[纳拉甘西特|纳拉甘西特]]（{{lang|en|Narragansett}}）海滩附近有一名男子因伊莎贝尔产生的强烈海浪而失足淹死，还被卷进大海<ref name="rincdc">{{cite web |author=NCDC |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Rhode Island |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。康涅狄格州官员联系了[[利奇菲尔德县_(康涅狄格州)|利奇菲尔德县]][[沃特敦_(康乃狄克州)|沃特敦]]（{{lang|en|Watertown}}）的一家自来水公司以及[[纽黑文县_(康涅狄格州)|纽黑文县]][[切希尔_(康涅狄格州)|切希尔]]（{{lang|en|Cheshire}}）的一家杂货店，向他们募捐来对[[飓风伊莎贝尔对北卡罗莱纳州的影响|北卡罗莱纳州]]受到影响的居民提供援助。伊莎贝尔登岸数天后，政府用拖车向北卡罗莱纳州送去了7570公升饮用水和11340公斤冰块<ref name="cema">{{cite web |author=Office of Governor Rell |year=2003 |title=Connecticut Pitches In To Help North Carolina Hurricane Victims--2,000 Gallons of Water, 25,000 Pounds of Ice On Its Way South |accessdate=2014-02-15 |url=http://www.ct.gov/governorrell/cwp/view.asp?A=11&Q=260210 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517133912/http://www.ct.gov/governorrell/cwp/view.asp?A=11&Q=260210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。佛蒙特州也因风暴和高压脊之间的压力梯度而出现大风，其中阵风时速最高的是在欢乐谷（{{lang|en|Pleasant Valley}}）达到的89公里，导致该州局部区域有树木和供电线路被刮倒<ref name="verncdc1">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003|title=Event Report for Vermont |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。[[齊坦丹縣|齊坦丹縣]]的[[里士满_(佛蒙特州)|里士特]]（{{lang|en|Richmond}}）有三辆卡车被倒塌的树木砸伤<ref name="verncdc2">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (2) |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>，[[阿迪森县|阿迪森县]]的[[索尔兹伯里_(佛蒙特州)|索尔兹伯里]]（{{lang|en|Salisbury}}）也有一辆汽车因树木倒塌受损<ref name="verncdc3">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (3) |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。佛蒙特州遭受的经济损失约为10万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|100000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="verncdc1"/><ref name="verncdc2" /><ref name="verncdc3" /><ref name="verncdc4">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (4) |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc5">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (5) |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc6">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (6) |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2014-02-08 |deadurl= yes |url= http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。此外，[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]和缅因州均有多个地区的降雨量达到25毫米<ref name="rain" />。

